Text: yeah i get that :( you binge really hard and then feel guilty for binging so you restrict. i feel ya :(

Author: lauryleah
Text: i think if i'll ever get diagnosed it would be non purging bulimia  I'm binging like crazy for one day and then fast for the rest of the week :( it really is a vicious cycle i can't get out of :(
